Prepare to Install the OmniStudio Package

Before you can install an OmniStudio package, you must prepare your browser and your Salesforce org. If you're upgrading OmniStudio, you can skip this task.

Verify that your web browser and Salesforce version meet at least these minimum requirements:

* Your browser works with OmniStudio.
* Your system has a minimum of 4 GB of RAM.
* Your browser has JavaScript enabled.
* Your Salesforce Edition is Enterprise, Unlimited, or Performance.
* You have the OmniStudio permission set license and optionally licenses for Foundation Document Generation.
* You have a valid subscription to Salesforce Customer Community, Salesforce Customer Community Plus, or Salesforce Partner Community.

Make sure the admin user has your email. If not, create a new user with System Administrator profile.

Enable Orders, Salesforce CRM content, Enhanced Email, and ensure email deliverability access level is set to All email.

title: Preparing Salesforce Org for OmniStudio Installation
